fields.name: AllowCredentials
fields.description: Whether user credentials are supported on cross-site requests. Valid values: `true`, `false`.

fields.name: AllowedHeaders
fields.description: Allowed headers in cross-site requests. The special value `*` allows actual requests to send any header.

fields.name: AllowedMethods
fields.description: Allowed HTTP methods on cross-site requests. The special value `*` allows all methods. If not set, `GET` and `HEAD` are allowed by default.

fields.name: AllowedOriginPatterns
fields.description: Allowed origin patterns to make cross-site requests.

fields.name: AllowedOrigins
fields.description: Allowed origins to make cross-site requests. The special value `*` allows all domains.

fields.name: ExposedHeaders
fields.description: HTTP response headers to expose for cross-site requests.

fields.name: MaxAge
fields.description: How long, in seconds, the response from a pre-flight request can be cached by clients.
